defaultDepartment for Environment, Food and Rural Affair’s 
defaultnew 
default‘
defaultEvidence Investment Strategy
default’
default defaultis currently being developed and has used an analysis of horizon scanning sources along with input from policy makers, evidence specialists and independent experts to identify key strategic challenges for the department. This will ensure 
defaultthe department’s
default evidence strategy takes a comprehensive and strategic view of evidence needs, and accounts for em
defaulterging opportunities and risks
